

    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header-section" >

        <h1>Sabbath House</h1>
        <p>Come...that God may refresh you</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section id="events" class="events-section">
            <div class="container">
      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <h1>Events</h1>
                </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-0 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 event event-fall">
          <%= link_to image_tag("/assets/images/fall-big.png"), pages_path("fallfridays") %>
          <h2>Fall Fridays</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-0 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 event event-bereavement" >
          <%= link_to image_tag("/assets/images/woods-big.png"),pages_path("bereavement") %>
          <h2>Bereavement Ministry</h2>
       </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-0 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 event event-prayer">
          <%= link_to image_tag("/assets/images/pray-big.png"), pages_path("eveningprayer") %>
          <h2>Evening Prayer</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-0 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 event event-lent">
          <%= link_to image_tag("/assets/images/lent.png"), pages_path("lent2017") %>
          <h2>Lent 2017 - Say Yes</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="retreats" class="retreats-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
            <h1>Retreats</h1>
            If you are interested in a fall retreat offering, 
            <%= mail_to "camille@sabbathhouseministry.org", "camille@sabbathhouseministry.org", subject:"Sabbath House Retreat Inquiry" %>. Leave your name, number and a message to schedule retreat days this January 2017. These retreats may be scheduled personally, as couples, or as groups. You may choose from the following offerings:
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <div class="retreat">
                      <%= image_tag("/assets/images/plant-64.png") %>
                      <div class="retreat-text">
                      <p class="retreat-title">Becoming More by Doing Less</p>
                      <p class="retreat-by">by Terry Hershey</p>
                      <p class="retreat-desc">Exploring the need and the blessing of choosing to live a Rhythm of Sabbath.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="retreat">
                      <%= image_tag("/assets/images/flame-64.png") %>
                      <div class="retreat-text">
                      <p class="retreat-title">Catching Fire, Becoming Flame</p>
                      <p class="retreat-by">by Albert Haase, OFM</p>
                      <p class="retreat-desc">Ever wonder how some people become enthusiastic and on fire about their relationship with God? Father Albert Haase gives you the tools and kindling to prepare for the spark of God in your life – and then shows you how to fan it into flame until you are set ablaze.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="retreat">
                      <%= image_tag("/assets/images/music-64.png") %>
                      <div class="retreat-text"> 
                      <p class="retreat-title">Sabbath: Restoring the Sacred Rhythm of Rest</p>
                      <p class="retreat-by">inspired by Wayne Mueller’s book on Sabbath</p>
                      <p class="retreat-desc">It has become our greeting: “I’m so busy.” His book seeks to heal our harried lives, and show us how to create a special time of rest, delight, and renewal – a refuge for our souls.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="musings" class="musings-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <h1>Musings on Keeping the Sabbath</h1>
                    <%= render 'pages/musings' %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 quote">
                    <i class="fa fa-5x fa-quote-left" aria-hidden="true"></i><span>The Sabbath House Ministry is a blessing to all who walk through the doors. It is place of peace and prayer. Attending Lenten retreats and listening to guest speakers have deepened my faith and given me a sense of closeness with others.  It is the perfect place to be still and listen.</span>
                    <p class="quote-by">Michelle</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-12 quote">
                    <span>Learning about Sabbath Rest has opened a pathway to God our Creator; it has strengthened my belief in belonging and longing to be part of the Body of Christ</span><i class="fa fa-5x fa-quote-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <p class="quote-by">Renee</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    </div> <!-- /container -->
